# SUPATH — optional live-data keys.
#
# SUPATH runs with none of these set: every source has a documented reference
# or simulated fallback, and the UI always says which mode it is in. Add keys
# here to move a source from "reference" / "simulated" to "live".
#
# Prices need NO key at all — Yahoo Finance (BZ=F / CL=F futures) is the
# primary source, used automatically, nothing to configure here. EIA below is
# only a fallback for if Yahoo is ever unreachable.

# aisstream.io — free account, real-time AIS positions.
# Without this, the corridor simulator drives realistic tanker traffic instead.
AISSTREAM_API_KEY=

# VesselAPI.com — free tier (150 requests/month, no card). A second, partial
# live-AIS layer: real but unclassified AIS contacts inside two narrow windows
# (Hormuz approach, Gulf of Kutch approach), refreshed every 12h. Used only
# when aisstream is not connected; the corridor simulator still fills every
# corridor these two small windows don't reach. Get a key at vesselapi.com —
# no card required for the free tier.
VESSELAPI_KEY=

# EIA Open Data — free registration, Brent/WTI daily *spot* prices. Only used
# as a fallback if Yahoo Finance (the primary, keyless source) is ever
# unreachable — you do not need this for prices to work. Note: EIA reports
# the physical spot price, a different, equally legitimate benchmark from the
# futures price Yahoo and most tickers show; the two can genuinely differ by
# a few dollars. That's expected, not a bug.
EIA_API_KEY=

# GDELT Cloud (gdeltcloud.com) — optional, a different, newer, paid-signup
# product from the free GDELT DOC 2.0 API this app already uses (that one
# needs no key at all — nothing to configure there). GDELT Cloud adds real
# classified Conflict Events with Goldstein-scale severity, which enriches
# (not replaces) the news signal on the Risk Intelligence tab when set. Sign
# up free at gdeltcloud.com/auth/sign-up, generate a key from dashboard
# settings (format gdelt_sk_...). Note: GDELT Cloud's Maritime & Trade
# endpoints — chokepoint transits, dark-vessel detection — would be a great
# fit here but are gated behind a paid plan tier; this app does not call them.
GDELT_CLOUD_API_KEY=

# OpenSanctions — free tier available, broadens counterparty screening beyond
# the OFAC SDN CSV (which requires no key).
OPENSANCTIONS_API_KEY=

# Anthropic — used only for an optional prose-fluency pass over the advisor's
# brief. The advisor's numbers, posture and recommendations are computed
# without it; this key only affects how the narrative reads. It is never
# permitted to invent a figure that isn't already in the brief.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
